# ============================================
# CodeWhale .cursorignore
# Excludes files that AI agents don't need to read
# ============================================

# Build artifacts (~6.1G)
target/

# Frontend / non-Rust code
web/
npm/
extensions/
integrations/

# Lock files (7000+ lines, wasteful tokens)
Cargo.lock
package-lock.json
web/package-lock.json
extensions/vscode/package-lock.json
integrations/*/package-lock.json
flake.lock

# Large generated files
crates/tui/assets/model_catalog.bundled.json
crates/config/assets/models_dev.bundled.json

# Changelogs (historical records, don't affect code understanding)
CHANGELOG.md
docs/CHANGELOG_ARCHIVE.md
crates/tui/CHANGELOG.md

# Non-core documentation
docs/rfcs/
docs/evidence/
docs/skills/
benchmark_results/
ARCHITECTURE_REFORM.md
HIGHLIGHTS.md
USERGUIDE.md
SECURITY.md
docs/RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md
docs/RELEASE_RUNBOOK.md
docs/OPERATIONS_RUNBOOK.md
docs/V0_8_61_EXECUTION.md
docs/V0865_RELEASE_LEDGER.md
docs/V0865_REMAINING_AGENT_PROMPT.md

# Nix configuration
flake.nix
nix/

# Deployment configuration
deploy/
Dockerfile
.devcontainer/

# GitHub templates/workflows (agents don't need these)
.github/workflows/
.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/
.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md
.github/APPROVED_CONTRIBUTORS
.github/AUTHOR_MAP
.github/CODEOWNERS
.github/dependabot.yml
.github/FUNDING.yml

# Temporary/generated files
*.sh
*.cmd
!scripts/**
result.json
count_deps.py
project_overhaul_prompt.md

# ============================================
# KEPT (not excluded):
# - crates/ (Rust source code)
# - scripts/ (useful scripts)
# - docs/ core docs (ARCHITECTURE.md, CONFIGURATION.md, PROVIDERS.md)
# - assets/ directories
# - config.example.toml
# ============================================
